I was pleasantly surprised with this hotel, they let me come and check in at 9am when I was just off a cruise ship.	A call to the desk got the reassurance that cots were only brought to the rooms after check in - it would be there soon.	Upon arrival there was no where to park for check-in, so I was forced to double park and risk a ticket.	We used the computer room and found it fully stocked and we were able to get boarding passes for the return flight and check email with no problem.